    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称他已准备好不受欢迎以应对英国的挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/starmer-says-he-s-ready-to-be-unpopular-to-tackle-uk-challenges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默表示，他将做出“艰难的长期决定”来改革英国，修复该国的公共财政。这是自英国工党在 7 月大选中获胜以来，他首次在工党年度会议上发表讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/starmer-says-he-s-ready-to-be-unpopular-to-tackle-uk-challenges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:55:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利准备出售邮政股份以筹集约 24 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/italy-preparing-to-sell-poste-stake-to-raise-about-2-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 准备出售意大利邮政公司 (Poste Italiane SpA) 高达 15% 的股份，作为旨在削减该国巨额债务的私有化举措的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/italy-preparing-to-sell-poste-stake-to-raise-about-2-4-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:47:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊计划在四年内将债务削减至 2009 年以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/greece-aims-to-slash-debt-to-lowest-since-2009-within-four-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊财政部长表示，希腊计划在短短四年内削减约 20% 的债务，这是摆脱长达十年的债务危机的又一个里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/greece-aims-to-slash-debt-to-lowest-since-2009-within-four-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列力争在不发动地面战争的情况下击退真主党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-aims-to-force-back-hezbollah-without-starting-lebanon-ground-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去一周，以色列每天都对黎巴嫩境内的真主党发动袭击 —— 从暗杀指挥官到摧毁导弹发射器 —— 官员们表示，以色列此举意在迫使该组织从边境撤退，并停止火箭弹袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-aims-to-force-back-hezbollah-without-starting-lebanon-ground-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:20:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯考虑增加英国儿童保育资金以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uk-eyes-childcare-funding-boost-as-reeves-pledges-growth-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 正在考虑一项扩大儿童保育服务的资金方案，这是英国财政大臣在预算中提出的促进增长的措施之一，人们普遍预计该预算将以增税为主。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uk-eyes-childcare-funding-boost-as-reeves-pledges-growth-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 12:31:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克总理将罢免内阁青年党领袖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/czech-premier-moves-to-oust-of-junior-party-leader-from-cabinet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克总理彼得·菲亚拉 (Petr Fiala) 更换了来自小执政党的一名内阁部长，这一迹象表明在上周的地区选举中失败后，联合政府内部的紧张局势加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/czech-premier-moves-to-oust-of-junior-party-leader-from-cabinet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 11:29:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国财政部长林德纳加入对裕信银行的批评行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/germany-s-lindner-says-unicredit-rattled-commerzbank-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳 (Christian Lindner) 对意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit Spa) 增持德国商业银行 (Commerzbank AG) 股份的方式进行了批评，凸显了德国政府对这家意大利银行意外举动的恼怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/germany-s-lindner-says-unicredit-rattled-commerzbank-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:32:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩真主党造成 500 多人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-s-bombing-of-hezbollah-targets-kills-hundreds-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对真主党目标进行了更多空袭，这是自 2006 年双方爆发灾难性战争以来，以色列对黎巴嫩实施的最严重、伤亡最惨重的轰炸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-s-bombing-of-hezbollah-targets-kills-hundreds-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言对约翰迪尔征收关税以保住美国就业岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/trump-vows-to-call-xi-if-elected-press-him-to-honor-trade-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一场有关美国农民和贸易的活动上，前总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁说，如果美国农业机械制造商迪尔公司将生产转移到墨西哥，他将对其征收高额关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/trump-vows-to-call-xi-if-elected-press-him-to-honor-trade-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 19:45:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
